*.lnk

### Linux
# Backup files
*~

# Temporary files from deleted open files
.fuse_hidden*

# KDE directory preferences
.directory

# Linux trash folder
.Trash-*

# NFS temporary files
.nfs*

### VisualStudio
# User-specific files
*.suo
*.user

# Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

